{"tid":2371452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾七成半區議員曾被民政拖數　有人被拖$30萬戶口僅餘$1,100","createTime":"2021-01-19T01:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T02:48:32.000Z","uid":271829,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77610e629d7b3ae78e893d663afcd4d21518cbcb","tid":2371452,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JAKFo3RZoePLHUP2FkEQNK7_7Bk=/6000x4000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LTELHKSNVJEF5HBJFRDISMK66Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJAKFo3RZoePLHUP2FkEQNK7_7Bk%3D%2F6000x4000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLTELHKSNVJEF5HBJFRDISMK66Q.JPG&h=b5c3ac9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李志宏做過多年議助，有多年「claim錢」經驗，不明白為何上任後津貼久久未能成功申領。周智堅攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n現時區議員要維持辦事處運作，須先行墊支辦事處水電費、議員助理薪金及印刷宣傳品費用等，之後再向民政事務總署申請領取營運開支津貼。《蘋果》在上月底透過電郵，向全港300多名民主派區議員發放問卷，希望了解去年1月至11月，民政總署拖欠議員津貼的狀況。最終收回78份問卷，當中超過七成半，即60名區議員指，曾被民政總署拖欠發放津貼。<br />\n<br />\n有區議員指，一般申領津貼後約兩星期，署方便會發還相關款項，不過被拖欠津貼的區議員，就被拖欠1個月至11個月不等。最多人被拖欠5個月至6個月，其次就是有8名區議員反映的10至11個月，即有可能相關款項由上任至去年12月仍未能領取。而最多議員被拖欠1萬至5萬元，共有23人；有7人被拖欠20萬元或以上款項。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/IRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FIRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=ab7a2e44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FIRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4%2F&h=3087601e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/IRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4/</a>"},{"pid":"a028ad4ecaccd75cad6e83e0ccfee190c21f90dd","tid":2371452,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f2ccd757